text: The Kyselka Spa (; ), older name Kysibl, is a group of former public baths. It is in the village of Kyselka near Karlovy Vary in the Czech Republic. ==Other websites== *Zachraňte lázně Kyselka! – by ASORKD Category:Spa towns in the Czech Republic Category:Buildings and structures in the Czech Republic
